    "description": {
      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "Outcome A related:\r\n\t•  Economically poor and socially disadvantaged are trained and engaged in tested production\r\n\t    technologies of riverbed farming\r\n\t•  A local support system for technical and inputs supply is established.\r\n\t•  Agriculture, Forestry and Environment Committees are formed/mobilised to support local level\r\n\t    extension services to riverbed farmers\r\n\t•  Riverbed farmers have the capacity to develop as agro-enterprises\r\n\t•  Innovations related to riverbed farming are tested\r\n\t\r\n\tOutcome B related:\r\n\t• The potential for riverbed farming in the entire Tarai is assessed through riverbed mapping\r\n\t• The Riverbed Farming Alliance has the capacity to promote riverbed farming with the Government of\r\n\t    Nepal\r\n\t• A promotion strategy for riverbed farming is developed and implemented\r\n\t• A riverbed farming policy and guideline is drafted in collaboration between the Government of Nepal and the Riverbed Farming Alliance"
      },
      "ne": null
